<p>Changes include:</p>
<ul>
<li>Changed 'Retention' to 'Possession'</li>
<li>Removed link to SCP-1732, since it does not directly relate to SCP-1732</li>
<li>Used the on-site links instead of external links for crosslinking friendliness</li>
<li>Added a link to SCP-2456 since it fits with the Taiping Rebellion</li>
<li>Scaled down the American front to North and Central America</li>
<li>Added a collaborative supplement</li>
</ul>

